12"></a><a href="#_ftnref12">[12]</a><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt">Department of Health, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">Good practice in Continence Services</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt">, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt">April </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt">2000</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn13"></a><a href="#_ftnref13">[13]</a><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt"> House of Lords Select Committee on Public Service and Demographic Change, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">Ready for Ageing</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt">?, March 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a name="_ftn14"></a><a href="#_ftnref14">[14]</a><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt"> Care Quality Commission, </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt; font-style:italic">Health care in care homes: A special review of the provision of health care to those in care homes</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:9pt">, March 2012</span></p></body></html>